<script type="text/javascript">

  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'LNB_MDI_MODULE',
    function: function (self, api) {

      //=== (20201106,김정삼) MDI 메뉴 트리 스크롤
      var $treeScroll = $('.lnb_tree_box');
      $treeScroll.slimscroll({
        size: '5px',
        width: 'auto',
        height: '617px',
        color: '#a4afc1',
        railVisible: false,
        railColor: '#313946',
        railOpacity: 1,
        alwaysVisible: true,
        disableFadeOut: true,
        distance: 2
      });
      //===/

      //=== 4 이하 초기화
      $('.lnb_tree_root', $treeScroll).find('ul').css('display','none');
    }
  });

</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'FINDER_COMPONENT_isuCd_finder_stkisu0_0',
    init: 'init',
    mdi: {
      name: mdc.module.getMdiModuleName()
    },
    function: function (self, api) {
      var $content = api.getModuleNode();
      var $sel = $content.select;
	    var locale = "ko_KR";

      self.init = function () {
        
        var input = {
          lang: 'ko_KR',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          typeNo: '0'
        };
        var cookie = mdc.util.getFinderStorage(input);
        if(cookie.finderCd === 'finder_stkisu'){
          // typeNo별 쿠키종목을 구분해야하는 경우(ex 증권상품)를 위해 분기
          var typeNo = cookie.typeNo; //쿠키저장시 finder의 typeNo
          if(!typeNo){
            typeNo = '0';
          }
          if(typeNo == ('0')){
            if(cookie.codeVal)$sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(cookie.codeVal);
            if(cookie.tbox){
              $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(cookie.tbox);
            }
            if(cookie.codeNm)$sel('#codeNmisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(cookie.codeNm);
            if(cookie.codeVal2)$sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_02').val(cookie.codeVal2);

            
          }
        }

        
      };

      

      $sel('#btnisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').on('click', function () {

        if($sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val()==""){
          self.openFinder(false);
        }else{
          self.openFinder(true);
        }

      });

      $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').on('keydown', function (e) {
        if (13 == e.keyCode) {
          if($sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val()==""){
            self.openFinder(false);
          }else{
            self.openFinder(true);
          }

        }
      });

      self.openFinder = function (isKeyDown) {
        var s_tboxNmVal = '';

        //검색텍스트박스값의 변경이 없을 경우 검색어 안넘어가도록 (전체 검색 개념)
        var s_defaultVal = '005930/삼성전자';
        var input = {
          lang: 'ko_KR',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          typeNo: '0'
        };
        var s_tbox = api.util.getFinderStorage(input);

        if(s_tbox.tbox !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val() && s_defaultVal !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val()){
          s_tboxNmVal = $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val();
        }

        var params = {
          finderNo: '_finder_stkisu0_0',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          typeNo: '0',
          compValue: '',
          param1 : $sel('#param1isuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(),
          tboxId : 'tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0',
          tboxNm : s_tboxNmVal,
          codeValId : 'isuCd_finder_stkisu0_0',
          codeNmId : 'codeNmisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0',
          pnlid : '',
          disableCompValue: '',
          initSearch: 'false'
        };

        if(!isKeyDown){
          params.tboxNm = '';
        }

        if(mdc.validate.checkSearchText(params.tboxNm)){
          //= (20201120, 김정삼) 자동검색 목록을 선택목록 엔터키 입력 시 검색기 팝업 하지 않는다.
          //  >>> 개발담당자 로직 확인하자
          var $searchAuto = $sel('.search-auto');
          var visble = $searchAuto.is(':visible');
          // 목록에 1개 있을 때 enter 키인시 선택
          if ( visble && $searchAuto.find('li').length == 1 ) {
            $searchAuto.find('li').addClass('on');
          }
          var $selLi = $searchAuto.find('li.on');

          if ( visble && $selLi.length ) {
            $('a', $selLi).click();

            

            return false;
          }
          //=/
					
					if(params.finderCd == "finder_drvetcidx"){
	          mdc.layer.openModal({
	              appendTo: $content.getNode(),
	              className: 'pop_opened pop_opened1',
	              id: 'jsLayer_finder_stkisu0_0',
	              title: '주식 종목 검색',
	              width: 563,
	              height: 530,
	              url: '/comm/finder/finder_stkisu.jsp',
	              useCloseButton: false,
	              ajaxOption: {data: params},
	              focus: $(this),
	              afterAppend: function () {
	                api.module.getModule('FINDER_LAYER__finder_stkisu0_0').procInit();
	              }
	            });
					} else {          
	          mdc.layer.openModal({
	            appendTo: $content.getNode(),
	            className: 'pop_opened pop_opened1',
	            id: 'jsLayer_finder_stkisu0_0',
	            title: '주식 종목 검색',
	            width: 548,
	            height: 'auto',
	            url: '/comm/finder/finder_stkisu.jsp',
	            useCloseButton: false,
	            ajaxOption: {data: params},
	            focus: $(this),
	            afterAppend: function () {
	              api.module.getModule('FINDER_LAYER__finder_stkisu0_0').procInit();
	            }
	          });
					}
        }
      };

      
      
      var isEmptyCodeVal = false;
      $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').on('keyup', function (e) {
        if ( e.keyCode != 13 && !isEmptyCodeVal) {

          var s_defaultVal = '005930/삼성전자';
          var input = {
            lang: 'ko_KR',
            finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
            typeNo: '0'
          };
          var s_tbox = api.util.getFinderStorage(input);

          if(s_tbox.tbox === '' && s_defaultVal === ''){
            isEmptyCodeVal = true;
          }
          else {
            if(s_tbox.tbox !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val() && s_defaultVal !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val()){
              $sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val("");
              $sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_02').val("");
              isEmptyCodeVal = true;
            }
          }

        }
      });
      
    }
  });



  
  $.fn.defaultAutocomplete = $.fn.autocomplete;

  $.fn.autocomplete = function (options) {

    var _this = this;
    var isMouseUnder = false;

    var config = {
      'contextName' : 'output',
      'viewCount' : 7,
      'bldPath' : '',
      'submit' : undefined,
      'listFn' : undefined,
      'className' : 'search-auto',
      'submitClear' :  true,
      'searchCookie' : false,
      'searchCookieType' : '',
      'enterSubmit' : false,
      'param' : { }
    };

    if (options != null && options !== undefined) {
      $.extend(config, options);
    }

    var $searchAuto = $('<div></div>', {
      'class' : config.className,
      'css' : {
        'display' : 'none'
      }
    });

    $(_this).after($searchAuto);

    var submit = function (obj) {
      if (config.submit) {
        config.submit(obj);
      }
      $searchAuto.html('');
      $searchAuto.hide();
      if (config.submitClear) {
        $(_this).val('');
      }
    };

    $(_this).focusout(function () {
      if (!isMouseUnder) {
        $searchAuto.hide();
      }
    });

    $(_this).keyup(function (e) {
      if ((47 < e.keyCode && e.keyCode < 106) || (185 < e.keyCode && e.keyCode < 223) || (105 < e.keyCode && e.keyCode < 112) || 8 == e.keyCode || 46 == e.keyCode){
        if (!config.searchCookie){
          getSearchList();
        }
      }

      if (13 == e.keyCode && config.enterSubmit) {
        submit($searchAuto.find('li[data-selected=true]'));
      }

    });

    $(_this).keydown(function (e) {
      if(e.keyCode == 40) {
        var selected = $searchAuto.find('li[data-selected=true]');
        if (selected.length == 1) {
          selected.removeAttr('data-selected');
          selected.removeClass('on');

          var next = selected.next();
          next.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          next.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(next.children('a').text());
        } else {
          var first = $searchAuto.find('li:first');
          first.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          first.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(first.children('a').text());
        }
      }else if(e.keyCode == 38){
        var selected = $searchAuto.find('li[data-selected=true]');
        if (selected.length == 1) {
          selected.removeAttr('data-selected');
          selected.removeClass('on');

          var prev = selected.prev();
          prev.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          prev.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(prev.children('a').text());
        } else {
          var last = $searchAuto.find('li:last');
          last.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          last.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(last.children('a').text());
        }
      }
    }).click(function(e){
      if (config.searchCookie){
        if(Cookies.get(config.searchCookieType) != undefined){
          var schSaveData = Cookies.getJSON(config.searchCookieType);
          $ul = $('<ul></ul>');
          $.each(schSaveData, function(i, item){
            $ul.append('<li data-cd=\"'+ item.keyCd +'\" data-fcd=\"'+ item.KeyFullCd +'\" data-nm=\"'+ item.codNm +'\"><a href=\"#\">'+item.title+'</a></li>');
          });
          $searchAuto.html($ul);
          attachListEvent();
          $searchAuto.show();
        }
      }
    });

    var attachListEvent = function () {
      var li = $searchAuto.find('li');
      li.find('a').click(function () {
        submit($(this).parent());
        return false;
      });

      li.find('a').focusout(function () {
        $searchAuto.hide();
      });

      li.find('a').focus(function () {
        $searchAuto.show();
      });

      $searchAuto.find('ul').mouseleave(function () {
        isMouseUnder = false;
      });

      li.mouseenter(function () {
        li.removeAttr('data-selected');
        li.removeClass('on');
        var t = $(this);
        t.addClass('on');
        t.attr('data-selected', 'true');
        $(_this).val(t.children('a').text());
        isMouseUnder = true;
      });
    };

    var getSearchList = function () {
      var data = {
        'contextName' : config.contextName,
        'value' : encodeURIComponent($(_this).val()),
        'viewCount' : config.viewCount,
        'bldPath' : config.bldPath
      };
      $.extend(data, config.param);
      $.ajax({
        'url' : '/comm/finder/autocomplete.jspx',
        'data' : data,
        'success' : function (html) {
          if (html == '') {
            $searchAuto.hide();
          } else {
            var ul = '<ul>'+html+'</ul>';
            $searchAuto.html(ul);
            if (config.listFn) {
              config.listFn($searchAuto);
            }
            attachListEvent();
            $searchAuto.show();
          }
        }
      });
    };
  };

  $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').autocomplete({
    'contextName' : 'finder_stkisu',
    'bldPath' : '/dbms/comm/finder/finder_stkisu_autocomplete',
    'viewCount' : 5,
    'submit' : function (li) {
      var shotCd = li.attr('data-tp');
      var fullCd = li.attr('data-cd');
      var codeNm = li.attr('data-nm');
      var mktNm = 'ALL';

      $('#codeNmisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(li.attr('data-nm'));
      $('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(li.attr('data-cd'));
      $('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_02').val(li.attr('data-tp'));

      // 지수면 명칭만
      if ( 'ISU' === 'IDX' ) {
        $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(li.attr('data-nm'));
      }
      // 회사면 발행기관 코드
      else if ( 'ISU' === 'COM' ) {
        $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(li.attr('data-cd')+'/'+li.attr('data-nm'));
      }
      // 그외 코드/명칭
      else {
        $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_0').val(li.attr('data-tp')+'/'+li.attr('data-nm'));
      }

      var input = {
        lang: 'ko_KR',
        finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
        tbox: shotCd +'/'+ codeNm,
        codeNm: codeNm,
        codeVal: fullCd,
        codeVal2: fullCd,
        typeNo: '',
        param1: mktNm
      };

      //= (20201202, 김정삼)
      if ( 'ISU' === 'IDX' ) {//지수
        input.tbox = codeNm;
        input.codeVal2 = shotCd;
      }
      //=/
      mdc.util.setFinderStorage(input);

      return false;
    },
    'submitClear' : false
  });
  
</script>

          </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

<span><dfn>컨텐츠 문의</dfn>&nbsp;:&nbsp;(유)주식시장부, &nbsp;(코)코스닥시장부, &nbsp;(넥)코넥스시장부, &nbsp;고객센터 (1577-0088)</span>

<script type="text/javascript">
  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'MDCSTAT021_0',
    init: 'init',
    mdi: {
      name: mdc.module.getMdiModuleName(),
      event: {
        afterViewActivated: ['resizeChart'],
        afterViewSizeChanged: ['resizeChart']
      }
    },
    function: function (self, api) {
      var $content = api.getModuleNode();
      var $f = $content.select('#MDCSTAT021_FORM');
      var $gridTable = $('#jsGrid_MDCSTAT021_0');
      var $grid;
      var mdiView = api.getMdiView();
      var menuId = mdiView ? mdiView.id : '';
      var pdfJsDelay = 5000;

      self.init = function () {
        self.grid = api.util.grid.init({
          node: api.getModuleNode().getNode(),
          form: $f,
          pdfJsDelay:pdfJsDelay,
          layout: 'no-apply',
          grid: [
            {
              menuIdForPdf: menuId
            }
          ]
        });

        $grid = $gridTable.initGrid({
          message: {
            emptyData: api.lang.getMessage('MD002')
          }
        });

        // 차트 스타일
        var chartStyle = $.extend(true, {}, webponent.chart.styles.lineCandle_bar);
        chartStyle.main.xAxis.gap = 13;

        // 차트
        self.chart = api.util.chart.init({
          node: api.getModuleNode().getNode(),
          form: $f,
          pdfJsDelay:pdfJsDelay,
          layout: 'no-apply',
          chart: {
            template: $content.select('#jsChart'),
            bld: [
              'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02105',
              'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02106&ddTp=1W',
              'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02106&ddTp=1M',
              'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02106&ddTp=3M',
              'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02106&ddTp=1Y',
              'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02106&ddTp=3Y'
            ],
            bldDataKey: 'output',
            options: webponent.chart.options.lineCandle_bar, //차트 옵션 및 데이터 설정
            styles: chartStyle, //차트 CSS 설정
            tipDataKey: [],
            series: { //차트 형태 및 X,Y축 기준 설정
              main: {
                s1: {series: 'line', form: 'updown_base', xaxis: 'TRD_DD', yaxis: 'TDD_CLSPRC', open: 'TDD_OPNPRC', high: 'TDD_HGPRC', low: 'TDD_LWPRC', close: 'TDD_CLSPRC', trade: 'ACC_TRDVOL'}
              },
              sub: {
                s1: {series: 'column', xaxis: 'TRD_DD', yaxis: 'ACC_TRDVOL', open: 'TDD_OPNPRC', high: 'TDD_HGPRC', low: 'TDD_LWPRC', close: 'TDD_CLSPRC', trade: 'ACC_TRDVOL'}
              }
            },
            maxData: {
              label: '15:30'
            },
            prevCloseFnm : 'BAS_PRC'
          },
          bigChart: {
            styles: webponent.chart.styles.lineCandle_bar_big,
            jqChartTtlSelector : '#MDCSTAT021_MDI_CONT .jsIdxNm'                // 빅차트 제목 전달을 위한 jq selecter
          }
        });

        var isuCd = '';
        if(isuCd !== ''){
          $content.select('[name=isuCd]').val(isuCd);
        }

        
        self.search();
      };

      //창 resize 이벤트 - 챠트용
      self.resizeChart = function () {
        self.chart.resize();
      };
      
      
      self.isuInfoBind = function () {
        var $isuInfoBind = $content.select('#isuInfoBind');
        var $isuInfoTitle = $content.select('#isuInfoTitle');

        api.util.submitAjax({
          url: '/comm/bldAttendant/getJsonData.cmd?bld=dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02101',
          data: $f.serialize(),
          success: function (resp) {
            $content.select('.CI-MDI-UNIT-TIME').html('<img src="/templets/mdc/img/ico_clock.png" alt="시계">'+ resp['CURRENT_DATETIME'] +'&nbsp;<span>('+ mdc.lang.getMessage('ME003') +')</span>');

            if(resp['ISU_NM']){
              resp['PER_PBR'] = resp['PER'] + '/' + resp['PBR'];

              api.util.singleDatabind($isuInfoBind, resp);

              $isuInfoTitle.empty();
              $isuInfoTitle.removeClass('kospi_red kospi_blue kospi_black');

              var flucShape = "";
              resp.CMPPREVDD_PRC = resp.CMPPREVDD_PRC.replace(/[^0-9.,]/g, '');

              if(resp.FLUC_TP_CD=="1" || resp.FLUC_TP_CD=="4"){
                $isuInfoTitle.addClass("kospi_red");
                flucShape = "▲";
                // $content.select('#TDD_OPNPRC').addClass("up");
                // $content.select('#TDD_HGPRC').addClass("up");
                // $content.select('#TDD_LWPRC').addClass("up");
                resp.FLUC_RT = '+'+resp.FLUC_RT;
              }
              else if(resp.FLUC_TP_CD=="2" || resp.FLUC_TP_CD=="5"){
                $isuInfoTitle.addClass("kospi_blue");
                flucShape = "▼";
                // $content.select('#TDD_OPNPRC').addClass("down");
                // $content.select('#TDD_HGPRC').addClass("down");
                // $content.select('#TDD_LWPRC').addClass("down");
              }
              else {
                $isuInfoTitle.addClass("kospi_black");
                flucShape = "";
              }

              var infoTitleHtml = '<label class="jsIdxNm cursor_df">' +  resp.ISU_NM + " ("+resp.ISU_SRT_CD+")</label> | " + resp.MKT_NM;
              if(resp.PRSNT_PRC !== '')
                infoTitleHtml += "<span>"+resp.PRSNT_PRC+"<dfn>"+flucShape+""+resp.CMPPREVDD_PRC+"&nbsp;("+resp.FLUC_RT+"%)</dfn></span>";

              $isuInfoTitle.append(infoTitleHtml);
            }

          }
        });
        
      };
      
      
      self.getList = function () {
        api.util.submitAjax({
          url: '/comm/bldAttendant/getJsonData.cmd?bld=dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02102',
          data: $f.serialize(),
          success: function (resp) {
            var data = resp['output'];
            data = {result: data};
            $grid.databind(data, 'result', {
              setFlucComp: api.util.setFlucComp,
              setFlucRate: api.util.setFlucRate
            });
          }
        });
      };
      

      
      self.ovrvwGenBind = function () {
        var $ovrvwGenBind = $content.select('#ovrvwGenBind');
        api.util.submitAjax({
          url: '/comm/bldAttendant/getJsonData.cmd?bld=dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02103',
          data: $f.serialize(),
          success: function (resp) {
            api.util.singleDatabind($ovrvwGenBind, resp);
          }
        });        
      };
      
      
      self.fsInfoBind = function () {
        var $fsInfoBind = $content.select('#fsInfoBind');
        api.util.submitAjax({
          url: '/comm/bldAttendant/getJsonData.cmd?bld=dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02104',
          data: $f.serialize(),
          success: function (resp) {
            api.util.singleDatabind($fsInfoBind, resp);
          }
        });
      };
      
      
      self.search = function () {
        var isuCd = $f.find('[name="isuCd"]').val();
        if(isuCd === ''){
          mdc.layer.alert(mdc.lang.getMessage('MG002'));
          return;
        }
        $content.select('.jsChgDate').find('li').eq(0).click();
        self.isuInfoBind();
        self.getList();
        self.ovrvwGenBind();
        self.fsInfoBind();
      };

      $f.find('[name="isuCd"]').on('change',function () {
        var input = {
          lang: 'ko_KR',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          typeNo: ''
        };
        var output = mdc.util.getFinderStorage(input);
        if(output.param1 && output.param1 === 'KNX'){
          $content.select('#jsOpenView_2').hide();
        }
        else {
          $content.select('#jsOpenView_2').show();
        }
      });

      self.getFinderInfo = function () {
        var input = {
          lang: 'ko_KR',
          finderCd: 'finder_secuprodisu',
          tbox: $f.find('input').val(),
          codeNm: $f.find('input').val(),
          codeVal: $f.find('[name=isuCd]').val(),
          codeVal2: $f.find('[name=isuCd]').val(),
          typeNo: '',
          param1: ''
        };
        mdc.util.setFinderStorage(input);
      }

      $content.select('#jsOpenView', $content.getNode()).on('click', function () {
        self.getFinderInfo();
        api.module.getMdiObject().closeView('MDC0201020103');
        api.module.getMdiObject().openView('MDC0201020103');
      });

      //투자자별 거래실적(개별종목)
      $content.select('#jsOpenView_1', $content.getNode()).on('click', function () {
        self.getFinderInfo();
        api.module.getMdiObject().closeView('MDC0201020302');
        api.module.getMdiObject().openView('MDC0201020302');
      });

      //PER/PBR/배당수익률(개별종목)
      $content.select('#jsOpenView_2', $content.getNode()).on('click', function () {
        self.getFinderInfo();
        api.module.getMdiObject().closeView('MDC0201020502');
        api.module.getMdiObject().openView('MDC0201020502', {searchType:'2'});
      });

      //외국인보유량(개별종목)
      $content.select('#jsOpenView_3', $content.getNode()).on('click', function () {
        self.getFinderInfo();
        api.module.getMdiObject().closeView('MDC0201020504');
        api.module.getMdiObject().openView('MDC0201020504', {searchType:'2'});
      });

    }  
    
    
  });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'FINDER_COMPONENT_isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1',
    init: 'init',
    mdi: {
      name: mdc.module.getMdiModuleName()
    },
    function: function (self, api) {
      var $content = api.getModuleNode();
      var $sel = $content.select;
	    var locale = "ko_KR";

      self.init = function () {
        
        var input = {
          lang: 'ko_KR',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          typeNo: '0'
        };
        var cookie = mdc.util.getFinderStorage(input);
        if(cookie.finderCd === 'finder_stkisu'){
          // typeNo별 쿠키종목을 구분해야하는 경우(ex 증권상품)를 위해 분기
          var typeNo = cookie.typeNo; //쿠키저장시 finder의 typeNo
          if(!typeNo){
            typeNo = '0';
          }
          if(typeNo == ('0')){
            if(cookie.codeVal)$sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(cookie.codeVal);
            if(cookie.tbox){
              $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(cookie.tbox);
            }
            if(cookie.codeNm)$sel('#codeNmisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(cookie.codeNm);
            if(cookie.codeVal2)$sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_12').val(cookie.codeVal2);

            
          }
        }

        
      };

      

      $sel('#btnisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').on('click', function () {

        if($sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val()==""){
          self.openFinder(false);
        }else{
          self.openFinder(true);
        }

      });

      $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').on('keydown', function (e) {
        if (13 == e.keyCode) {
          if($sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val()==""){
            self.openFinder(false);
          }else{
            self.openFinder(true);
          }

        }
      });

      self.openFinder = function (isKeyDown) {
        var s_tboxNmVal = '';

        //검색텍스트박스값의 변경이 없을 경우 검색어 안넘어가도록 (전체 검색 개념)
        var s_defaultVal = '005930/삼성전자';
        var input = {
          lang: 'ko_KR',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          typeNo: '0'
        };
        var s_tbox = api.util.getFinderStorage(input);

        if(s_tbox.tbox !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val() && s_defaultVal !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val()){
          s_tboxNmVal = $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val();
        }

        var params = {
          finderNo: '_finder_stkisu0_1',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          typeNo: '0',
          compValue: '',
          param1 : $sel('#param1isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(),
          tboxId : 'tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1',
          tboxNm : s_tboxNmVal,
          codeValId : 'isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1',
          codeNmId : 'codeNmisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1',
          pnlid : '',
          disableCompValue: '',
          initSearch: 'false'
        };

        if(!isKeyDown){
          params.tboxNm = '';
        }

        if(mdc.validate.checkSearchText(params.tboxNm)){
          //= (20201120, 김정삼) 자동검색 목록을 선택목록 엔터키 입력 시 검색기 팝업 하지 않는다.
          //  >>> 개발담당자 로직 확인하자
          var $searchAuto = $sel('.search-auto');
          var visble = $searchAuto.is(':visible');
          // 목록에 1개 있을 때 enter 키인시 선택
          if ( visble && $searchAuto.find('li').length == 1 ) {
            $searchAuto.find('li').addClass('on');
          }
          var $selLi = $searchAuto.find('li.on');

          if ( visble && $selLi.length ) {
            $('a', $selLi).click();

            
                if ( $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val() != '' ) {
                  mdc.module.getModule('MDCSTAT023_1')['search']($sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1'));
                }
            

            return false;
          }
          //=/
					
					if(params.finderCd == "finder_drvetcidx"){
	          mdc.layer.openModal({
	              appendTo: $content.getNode(),
	              className: 'pop_opened pop_opened1',
	              id: 'jsLayer_finder_stkisu0_1',
	              title: '주식 종목 검색',
	              width: 563,
	              height: 530,
	              url: '/comm/finder/finder_stkisu.jsp',
	              useCloseButton: false,
	              ajaxOption: {data: params},
	              focus: $(this),
	              afterAppend: function () {
	                api.module.getModule('FINDER_LAYER__finder_stkisu0_1').procInit();
	              }
	            });
					} else {          
	          mdc.layer.openModal({
	            appendTo: $content.getNode(),
	            className: 'pop_opened pop_opened1',
	            id: 'jsLayer_finder_stkisu0_1',
	            title: '주식 종목 검색',
	            width: 548,
	            height: 'auto',
	            url: '/comm/finder/finder_stkisu.jsp',
	            useCloseButton: false,
	            ajaxOption: {data: params},
	            focus: $(this),
	            afterAppend: function () {
	              api.module.getModule('FINDER_LAYER__finder_stkisu0_1').procInit();
	            }
	          });
					}
        }
      };

      
      
      var isEmptyCodeVal = false;
      $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').on('keyup', function (e) {
        if ( e.keyCode != 13 && !isEmptyCodeVal) {

          var s_defaultVal = '005930/삼성전자';
          var input = {
            lang: 'ko_KR',
            finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
            typeNo: '0'
          };
          var s_tbox = api.util.getFinderStorage(input);

          if(s_tbox.tbox === '' && s_defaultVal === ''){
            isEmptyCodeVal = true;
          }
          else {
            if(s_tbox.tbox !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val() && s_defaultVal !== $sel('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val()){
              $sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val("");
              $sel('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_12').val("");
              isEmptyCodeVal = true;
            }
          }

        }
      });
      
    }
  });



  
  $.fn.defaultAutocomplete = $.fn.autocomplete;

  $.fn.autocomplete = function (options) {

    var _this = this;
    var isMouseUnder = false;

    var config = {
      'contextName' : 'output',
      'viewCount' : 7,
      'bldPath' : '',
      'submit' : undefined,
      'listFn' : undefined,
      'className' : 'search-auto',
      'submitClear' :  true,
      'searchCookie' : false,
      'searchCookieType' : '',
      'enterSubmit' : false,
      'param' : { }
    };

    if (options != null && options !== undefined) {
      $.extend(config, options);
    }

    var $searchAuto = $('<div></div>', {
      'class' : config.className,
      'css' : {
        'display' : 'none'
      }
    });

    $(_this).after($searchAuto);

    var submit = function (obj) {
      if (config.submit) {
        config.submit(obj);
      }
      $searchAuto.html('');
      $searchAuto.hide();
      if (config.submitClear) {
        $(_this).val('');
      }
    };

    $(_this).focusout(function () {
      if (!isMouseUnder) {
        $searchAuto.hide();
      }
    });

    $(_this).keyup(function (e) {
      if ((47 < e.keyCode && e.keyCode < 106) || (185 < e.keyCode && e.keyCode < 223) || (105 < e.keyCode && e.keyCode < 112) || 8 == e.keyCode || 46 == e.keyCode){
        if (!config.searchCookie){
          getSearchList();
        }
      }

      if (13 == e.keyCode && config.enterSubmit) {
        submit($searchAuto.find('li[data-selected=true]'));
      }

    });

    $(_this).keydown(function (e) {
      if(e.keyCode == 40) {
        var selected = $searchAuto.find('li[data-selected=true]');
        if (selected.length == 1) {
          selected.removeAttr('data-selected');
          selected.removeClass('on');

          var next = selected.next();
          next.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          next.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(next.children('a').text());
        } else {
          var first = $searchAuto.find('li:first');
          first.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          first.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(first.children('a').text());
        }
      }else if(e.keyCode == 38){
        var selected = $searchAuto.find('li[data-selected=true]');
        if (selected.length == 1) {
          selected.removeAttr('data-selected');
          selected.removeClass('on');

          var prev = selected.prev();
          prev.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          prev.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(prev.children('a').text());
        } else {
          var last = $searchAuto.find('li:last');
          last.attr('data-selected', 'true');
          last.addClass('on');
          $(_this).val(last.children('a').text());
        }
      }
    }).click(function(e){
      if (config.searchCookie){
        if(Cookies.get(config.searchCookieType) != undefined){
          var schSaveData = Cookies.getJSON(config.searchCookieType);
          $ul = $('<ul></ul>');
          $.each(schSaveData, function(i, item){
            $ul.append('<li data-cd=\"'+ item.keyCd +'\" data-fcd=\"'+ item.KeyFullCd +'\" data-nm=\"'+ item.codNm +'\"><a href=\"#\">'+item.title+'</a></li>');
          });
          $searchAuto.html($ul);
          attachListEvent();
          $searchAuto.show();
        }
      }
    });

    var attachListEvent = function () {
      var li = $searchAuto.find('li');
      li.find('a').click(function () {
        submit($(this).parent());
        return false;
      });

      li.find('a').focusout(function () {
        $searchAuto.hide();
      });

      li.find('a').focus(function () {
        $searchAuto.show();
      });

      $searchAuto.find('ul').mouseleave(function () {
        isMouseUnder = false;
      });

      li.mouseenter(function () {
        li.removeAttr('data-selected');
        li.removeClass('on');
        var t = $(this);
        t.addClass('on');
        t.attr('data-selected', 'true');
        $(_this).val(t.children('a').text());
        isMouseUnder = true;
      });
    };

    var getSearchList = function () {
      var data = {
        'contextName' : config.contextName,
        'value' : encodeURIComponent($(_this).val()),
        'viewCount' : config.viewCount,
        'bldPath' : config.bldPath
      };
      $.extend(data, config.param);
      $.ajax({
        'url' : '/comm/finder/autocomplete.jspx',
        'data' : data,
        'success' : function (html) {
          if (html == '') {
            $searchAuto.hide();
          } else {
            var ul = '<ul>'+html+'</ul>';
            $searchAuto.html(ul);
            if (config.listFn) {
              config.listFn($searchAuto);
            }
            attachListEvent();
            $searchAuto.show();
          }
        }
      });
    };
  };

  $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').autocomplete({
    'contextName' : 'finder_stkisu',
    'bldPath' : '/dbms/comm/finder/finder_stkisu_autocomplete',
    'viewCount' : 5,
    'submit' : function (li) {
      var shotCd = li.attr('data-tp');
      var fullCd = li.attr('data-cd');
      var codeNm = li.attr('data-nm');
      var mktNm = 'ALL';

      $('#codeNmisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(li.attr('data-nm'));
      $('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(li.attr('data-cd'));
      $('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_12').val(li.attr('data-tp'));

      // 지수면 명칭만
      if ( 'ISU' === 'IDX' ) {
        $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(li.attr('data-nm'));
      }
      // 회사면 발행기관 코드
      else if ( 'ISU' === 'COM' ) {
        $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(li.attr('data-cd')+'/'+li.attr('data-nm'));
      }
      // 그외 코드/명칭
      else {
        $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(li.attr('data-tp')+'/'+li.attr('data-nm'));
      }

      var input = {
        lang: 'ko_KR',
        finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
        tbox: shotCd +'/'+ codeNm,
        codeNm: codeNm,
        codeVal: fullCd,
        codeVal2: fullCd,
        typeNo: '',
        param1: mktNm
      };

      //= (20201202, 김정삼)
      if ( 'ISU' === 'IDX' ) {//지수
        input.tbox = codeNm;
        input.codeVal2 = shotCd;
      }
      //=/
      mdc.util.setFinderStorage(input);

      return false;
    },
    'submitClear' : false
  });
  
</script>

      </tr>

<div class="cal-wrap"><div class="cal-area"><input type="text" name="strtDd" id="strtDd" value="20220701" maxlength="8"><span>~</span><input type="text" name="endDd" id="endDd" value="20220708" maxlength="8"><button type="button" class="cal-btn-open" data-calendar-module="true" data-calendar-display="false">달력열기</button><button type="button" class="cal-btn-range1d">1일</button><button type="button" class="cal-btn-range1m">1개월</button><button type="button" class="cal-btn-range6m">6개월</button><button type="button" class="cal-btn-range1y">1년</button></div></div>


<script type="text/javascript">
  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'SEARCH_COMPONENT__140831394',
    mdi: {
      name: mdc.module.getMdiModuleName()
    },
    function: function (self, api) {
      var $content = api.getModuleNode();
      var $element = $content.select('[name="endDd"]');

      
      var params = {
        baseName: 'krx.mdc.i18n.component',
        key: 'B122.bld',
        locale: 'ko'
      };

      var queryString = 'null';
      if (queryString && queryString !== 'null') {
        var queryArray = queryString.split('&');
        queryArray.forEach(function (query) {
          var name = query.split('=')[0];
          var value = query.split('=')[1] || '';
          params[name] = value;
        });
      }
      

      
        
          var calendarOption = {};
          var input = [];
          
            
              
              input.push($content.select('[name="strtDd"]'));
              
              input.push($content.select('[name="endDd"]'));
              
            
          

          
          var date = '';
          api.util.submitAjax({
            method: 'GET',
            url: '/comm/bldAttendant/executeForResourceBundle.cmd',
            async: false,
            data: params,
            success: function (data) {
              var output = data['result']['output'];
              output.forEach(function (item) {
                $.each(item, function (key, value) {
                  date = value;
                });
              });
            }
          });

          if (date) {
            input.forEach(function (item) {
              item.val(date);
            });

            //=== (20201028, 김정삼) compIdDateLimit 값을 지정한 경우 이 지정값(bld)으로 달력팝업활성화 종료일 기준을 변경한다
            
            calendarOption.limit = date;

            var compIdDateLimit = 'B128';
            var compId = 'B122';
            if (compIdDateLimit && compIdDateLimit !== compId) {
              api.util.submitAjax({
                method: 'GET',
                url: '/comm/bldAttendant/executeForResourceBundle.cmd',
                async: false,
                data: $.extend(params, {key: compIdDateLimit + '.bld'}),
                success: function (data) {
                  var output = data['result']['output'];
                  output.forEach(function (item) {
                    $.each(item, function (key, value) {
                      calendarOption.limit = value;
                    });
                  });
                }
              });
            }
            
            //===/

            //=== (20201215, 김상훈) restictId 값을 지정한 경우 이 지정값(bld)으로 조회가능 시작일을 제한한다.
            
            var restictId = 'B155';
            var menuId = mdc.getMdiView() ? mdc.getMdiView().id : '';

            if (restictId && (menuId !== '' && menuId !== undefined)) {
              params['menuId'] = menuId;
              api.util.submitAjax({
                method: 'GET',
                url: '/comm/bldAttendant/executeForResourceBundle.cmd',
                async: false,
                data: $.extend(params, {key: restictId + '.bld'}),
                success: function (data) {
                  var output = data['result']['output'];
                  calendarOption.restrictDate = output[0]['restrict_date'];
                }
              });
            }
            
            //===/

            
            // 기간 재계산
            var datePeriod = '-7d';
            var periodType = datePeriod.substring(datePeriod.length - 1); // +-d, +-m, +-y
            var period = Number(datePeriod.substring(0, datePeriod.length - 1));
            date = api.util.calcDate(date).getCalcDate(periodType, Math.abs(period));

            //변경된 시작일자가 영업일이 아닌경우 직전영업일로 일자 변경 (최한주:2021-08-25)
              
                  api.util.submitAjax({
                    method: 'GET',
                    url: '/comm/bldAttendant/executeForResourceBundle.cmd',
                    async: false,
                    data: $.extend(params, {key: 'B161' + '.bld', inDate: date}),
                    success: function (data) {
                      var output = data['result']['output'];
                      date = output[0]['bis_work_dt'];
                    }
                  });
              

              //20201215 김상훈, 달력 시작일자가 제한일보다 전일인 경우 제한일을 시작일로 설정
            if(calendarOption.restrictDate != undefined && date < calendarOption.restrictDate){
              date = calendarOption.restrictDate;
            }

            if (period >= 0) input[input.length - 1].val(date);
            else input[0].val(date);

            

          }
          

          calendarOption.input = input;
          calendarOption.positionTop = false;
          calendarOption.showButton = true;
          calendarOption.disabledDate = 'null';
          calendarOption.disabledTp = 'null';
          calendarOption.changeStrtDate = 'false';
          calendarOption.validatePeriodBusDate = 'B161';
          $.fn.calendar(calendarOption);
        

        
      

      

      
    }
  });
</script>

    </thead><tbody class="CI-GRID-BODY-TABLE-TBODY"><tr class="CI-GRID-EVEN">
      <td class="CI-GRID-ALIGN-CENTER" data-bind="INVST_TP_NM" data-name="INVST_TP_NM">금융투자</td>
      <td class="CI-GRID-ALIGN-RIGHT" data-bind="ASK_TRDVOL" data-name="ASK_TRDVOL">9,635,166</td>
      <td class="CI-GRID-ALIGN-RIGHT" data-bind="BID_TRDVOL" data-name="BID_TRDVOL">10,881,461</td>
      <td class="CI-GRID-ALIGN-RIGHT" data-bind="NETBID_TRDVOL" data-name="NETBID_TRDVOL">1,246,295</td>
      <td class="CI-GRID-ALIGN-RIGHT" data-bind="ASK_TRDVAL" data-name="ASK_TRDVAL">549,734,777,000</td>
      <td class="CI-GRID-ALIGN-RIGHT" data-bind="BID_TRDVAL" data-name="BID_TRDVAL">622,386,950,300</td>
      <td class="CI-GRID-ALIGN-RIGHT CI-GRID-CELL-LAST" data-bind="NETBID_TRDVAL" data-name="NETBID_TRDVAL">72,652,173,300</td>
    </tr><tr class="CI-GRID-ODD">

<span><dfn>컨텐츠 문의</dfn>&nbsp;:&nbsp;(유)주식시장부, &nbsp;(코)코스닥시장부, &nbsp;(넥)코넥스시장부, &nbsp;고객센터 (1577-0088)</span>


  












<p><span class="">주</span><span><dfn>당일 매매내역은 당일 정규시장 마감 이후(오후 3시45분 예정) 반영되며, 시간외 등의 매매내역이 포함된 최종 매매내역은 당일자 마감 이후(오후 6시 예정) 제공됩니다.</dfn></span></p>

  









<p><img src="/templets/mdc/img/blit_feel.png" alt="">&nbsp;본 정보는 투자참고 사항이며, 오류가 발생하거나 지연될 수 있습니다. 제공된 정보에 의한 투자결과에 대한 법적인 책임을 지지 않습니다.</p>

<script type="text/javascript">
  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'MDCSTAT023_1',
    init: 'init',
    mdi: {
      name: mdc.module.getMdiModuleName(),
      event: {
        afterViewActivated: ['resizeGrid'],
        afterViewSizeChanged: ['resizeGrid']
      }
    },
    function: function (self, api) {
      var $content = api.getModuleNode();
      var $f = $content.select('#MDCSTAT023_FORM');

      self.resizeGrid = function (e) {
        self.grid.setHeight(e.getContentLeftHeight());
        self.grid.resize();
      };

      self.init = function () {
        self.grid = api.util.grid.init({
          node: api.getModuleNode().getNode(),
          form: $f,
          layout: 'no-apply',
          grid: [
            {
              template: $content.select('#jsGrid_MDCSTAT023_0'),
              bld: 'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02301',
              bldDataKey: 'output',
              lateInfoYn: false,
              unit: {
                share: ['ASK_TRDVOL', 'BID_TRDVOL', 'NETBID_TRDVOL'],
                money: ['ASK_TRDVAL', 'BID_TRDVAL', 'NETBID_TRDVAL']
              },
              applyRowBg: false,
              customRowBg: {
                reference: 'CONV_OBJ_TP_CD',
                row: [
                  {
                    key: 'GB',
                    color: '#E4E4E4'
                  },
                  {
                    key: 'SS',
                    color: '#F8F8F8'
                  },
                  {
                    key: 'TS',
                    color: '#F0F0F0'
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              template: $content.select('#jsGrid_MDCSTAT023_1'),
              bld: 'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02302',
              bldDataKey: 'output',
              unit: {
                share: ['TRDVAL1', 'TRDVAL2', 'TRDVAL3', 'TRDVAL4', 'TRDVAL_TOT'],
                money: []
              }
            },
            {
              template: $content.select('#jsGrid_MDCSTAT023_2'),
              bld: 'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02302',
              bldDataKey: 'output',
              unit: {
                share: [],
                money: ['TRDVAL1', 'TRDVAL2', 'TRDVAL3', 'TRDVAL4', 'TRDVAL_TOT']
              }
            },
            {
              template: $content.select('#jsGrid_MDCSTAT023_3'),
              bld: 'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02303',
              bldDataKey: 'output',
              unit: {
                share: ['TRDVAL1', 'TRDVAL2', 'TRDVAL3', 'TRDVAL4', 'TRDVAL5', 'TRDVAL6', 'TRDVAL7', 'TRDVAL8', 'TRDVAL9', 'TRDVAL10', 'TRDVAL11', 'TRDVAL_TOT'],
                money: []
              }
            },
            {
              template: $content.select('#jsGrid_MDCSTAT023_4'),
              bld: 'dbms/MDC/STAT/standard/MDCSTAT02303',
              bldDataKey: 'output',
              unit: {
                share: [],
                money: ['TRDVAL1', 'TRDVAL2', 'TRDVAL3', 'TRDVAL4', 'TRDVAL5', 'TRDVAL6', 'TRDVAL7', 'TRDVAL8', 'TRDVAL9', 'TRDVAL10', 'TRDVAL11', 'TRDVAL_TOT']
              }
            }            
          ]
        });

        self.inqTpCdChg();
        self.search();
      };

      self.search = function () {
        var value = $f.find('[name="inqTpCd"]:checked').val();
        var detailChk = $f.find('[name="detailView"]').is(":checked");
        var trdVolVal = $f.find('[name="trdVolVal"]').val();

        if ($f.find('[name="isuCd"]').val() === '') {
          mdc.layer.alert(mdc.lang.getMessage('MG002'));
          return;
        }

        var index = 0;
        if (value === '1') index = 0;
        else if (value === '2' && trdVolVal === '1' && detailChk === false) index = 1;
        else if (value === '2' && trdVolVal === '2' && detailChk === false) index = 2;
        else if (value === '2' && trdVolVal === '1' && detailChk === true) index = 3;
        else if (value === '2' && trdVolVal === '2' && detailChk === true) index = 4;
        
        self.grid.setIndex(index); // 한 화면에 조건에 따라 다수의 그리드가 존재할 때 보여줄 그리드 인덱스 설정
        self.grid.show(); // 위에 설정한 인덱스의 그리드를 보여주고 다른 그리드는 모두 숨김
        self.grid.appendRow(); // 설정한 form 과 bld 를 바탕으로 서비스 조회 후 그리드에 데이터 삽입
        self.grid.resize(); // MDI 화면 특성 상 append 후 리사이즈 필수
      }
      
      self.inqTpCdChg = function () {
        var inqTpCd = $f.find('[name="inqTpCd"]:checked').val();
        if(inqTpCd=="1"){
          $f.find('[name="trdVolVal"]').hide();
          $f.find('[name="askBid"]').hide();
          $f.find('[name="detailView"]').closest('div').hide();
        }
        else {
          $f.find('[name="trdVolVal"]').show();
          $f.find('[name="askBid"]').show();
          $f.find('[name="detailView"]').closest('div').show();
        }

      }
      
      
    }
  });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">

  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'FINDER_LAYER__finder_stkisu0_1',
    init: 'init',
    function: function (self, api) {
      var $gridTable = $('#jsGrid__finder_stkisu0_1');
      var $grid;

      self.procInit = function () {
        self.setList();
      };
      
      self.setList = function () {
        if (!$grid) {
          $grid = $gridTable.initGrid({
            message: {
              emptyData: api.lang.getMessage('MJ008')
            },
            scroll: {
              maxRowCount: 7,
              autoHeight: true
            }
          });
        }

        var param = api.util.getSerializeObject($('#FORM__finder_stkisu0_1'));
        var searchText = param.searchText;
        var chkNo = searchText.indexOf('/');
        if(chkNo>0){//종목코드+종목명 조합시 -> 종목코드로 조회
          param.searchText = searchText.substr(0,chkNo);
        }
        self.setGridList(param);
      };

      self.setGridList = function (d) {

        if(mdc.validate.checkSearchText(d.searchText)) {
          d.bld = 'dbms/comm/finder/finder_stkisu';
          var d = mdc.validate.searchTextToConsonant(d);
          mdc.util.submitAjax({
            url: '/comm/bldAttendant/getJsonData.cmd',
            data: d,
            showLoading: true,
            success: function (resp) {
              var data = resp['block1'];

              //= (20201203, 김정삼) 한/영 전환키 오류로 한글을 영문으로 입력 오류 교정
              var value = d.searchText;
              var convertValue = (/^[a-zA-Z+]*$/.test(value)) ? AtoH.convert(value) : '';   // 전부영어(/^[a-zA-Z+]*$/)  영어포함(/[a-zA-Z]+/)
              if ( data.length == 0 && convertValue != '' ) {
                d.searchText = convertValue;
                mdc.util.submitAjax({
                  url: '/comm/bldAttendant/getJsonData.cmd',
                  data: d,
                  showLoading: true,
                  success: function (resp) {
                    var data = resp['block1'];
                    if(data && data.length === 1 && mdc.validate.engNumCheck($('[name=searchText]'))){
                      self.selectGridRow(data[0]);
                    }
                    else {
                      data = {result: data};
                      $grid.databind(data, 'result');
                    }
                  }
                });
              }
              else {
                if(data && data.length === 1 && mdc.validate.engNumCheck($('[name=searchText]'))){
                  self.selectGridRow(data[0]);
                }
                else {
                  data = {result: data};
                  $grid.databind(data, 'result');
                }

              }
              //=/
            }
          });
        }
      };
      
      
      $('#searchBtn__finder_stkisu0_1').on('click', function () {
        $('.btngrp__finder_stkisu0_1 li').prop("class","off");
        self.setList();
      });
      
      
      $('#jsGrid_div__finder_stkisu0_1').on('click', '#jsGrid__finder_stkisu0_1 .jsRow',  function () {
        // 행 데이터는 tbody에 data-keepdata="true" 옵션을 지정하면 각 행의 tr 마다 행의 데이터가 저장이 되어있다.
        if ( !self.selectGridRow(this.rowData) ) { return false; }
      });

      self.selectGridRow = function(data){
        if ( !data ) { return false; }
        var shotCd = data.short_code;
        var fullCd = data.full_code;
        var codeNm = data.codeName;
        var mktNm = data.marketCode;

        $('#tboxisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(shotCd +'/'+ codeNm);
        $('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(fullCd);
        $('#codeNmisuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').val(codeNm);

        var input = {
          lang: 'ko_KR',
          finderCd: 'finder_stkisu',
          tbox: shotCd +'/'+ codeNm,
          codeNm: codeNm,
          codeVal: fullCd,
          codeVal2: '',
          typeNo: '0',
          param1: mktNm
        };
        mdc.util.setFinderStorage(input);

        $('[name=' + $('#isuCd_finder_stkisu0_1').attr('name') + ']').trigger('change');

        api.layer.closeModal();
      };
      
      $('.btngrp__finder_stkisu0_1 li').on('click', function () {
        $('#searchText__finder_stkisu0_1').val('');      
        $('.btngrp__finder_stkisu0_1 li').prop("class","off");
        $(this).prop("class","on");
        
        var param = api.util.getSerializeObject($('#FORM__finder_stkisu0_1'));
        param.consonant = $(this).val();
        self.setGridList(param);
      });

      $('.btngrp__finder_stkisu0_1 li').on('keydown', function (e) {
        if(e.keyCode == 13){
          $('.btngrp__finder_stkisu0_1 li').prop("class","off");
          var param = api.util.getSerializeObject($('#FORM__finder_stkisu0_1'));
          param.consonant = $(this).val();
          self.setGridList(param);
        }
      });
      
      $('.mktsel__finder_stkisu0_1').on('change', function () {
        //self.setList();
      });
      
      $('#searchText__finder_stkisu0_1').on('keyup', function (event) {
        if(event.keyCode==13){
          $('.btngrp__finder_stkisu0_1 li').prop("class","off");
          var param = api.util.getSerializeObject($('#FORM__finder_stkisu0_1'));
          self.setGridList(param);          
        }
      });


      $('#thTr th').on('click',function(){
        $(this).find('a').click();
      })

      
    }
  });

</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
  mdc.module.setModule({
    name: 'MDI_MODULE',
    init: 'init',
    mdi: {
      isMdiModule: true
    },
    function: function (self, api) {

      var $searchResultWrap = $('#jsMdiSearchResultWrap');
      var $menuSearchValue = $('#jsMdiMenuSearchValue');
      var menuSearch = new api.util.MenuSearch('mdi', 1000);

      self.init = function () {
        // mdi 모듈 객체 로드
        self.mdi = api.getMdi();
        // mdi 모듈 초기화
        self.mdi.init($('.content'), $('#jsMdiMenu'), $('#jsMdiTab'), $('#jsMdiContent'));
        var params = {
          
          
          'menuId':'MDC0201020203',
          
          
        };
        if (params['menuId']) {
          self.mdi.openView(params['menuId'], params);
        }
      };

      // 메뉴검색
      var searchMenuList = function (value) {
        value = value.trim();
        var menus = menuSearch.searchMenu(value);
        if (menus.length > 0) {
          var menuName;
          var screenId;
          var screenNo;
          var menuPath;
          menus.forEach(function (menu) {
            menuName = menu['MENU_NM'] || '';
            screenId = menu['SCREN_ID'] || '';
            screenNo = menu['SCREN_NO'] || '';
            menuPath = menu['MENU_PATH'] ? menu['MENU_PATH'].replace(/>/gi, '<em>&gt;</em>') : '';
            $searchResultWrap.append($('<LI>').attr('data-menu-id', menu['MENU_ID']).append($('<SPAN>').append(screenNo)).append(menuPath)/*.append($('<DFN>')).append(menuName)*/);
          });
        } else {
          $searchResultWrap.append($('<LI>').text(mdc.lang.getMessage('MG027'))); //검색결과가 존재하지 않습니다.
        }

        $searchResultWrap.closest('div').show();
      };

      var getMenuIdByValue = function (value) {
        value = value.trim();
        var menu = menuSearch.searchCoincidentMenu(value) || {};
        return menu['MENU_ID'];
      };

      var openView = function (menuId) {
        self.mdi.openView(menuId);
        $menuSearchValue.val('');
        $searchResultWrap.closest('div').hide();
        $searchResultWrap.empty();
      };

      $menuSearchValue.on('keyup', _.debounce(function (e) {
        console.log(e.keyCode);
        // 엔터, ESC, 방향키
        if (e.keyCode === 13 || e.keyCode === 27 || (e.keyCode >= 37 && e.keyCode <= 40)) {
          e.preventDefault();
          return;
        }

        var value = this.value;
        $searchResultWrap.empty();
        if (value.length > 0) {
          searchMenuList(value);
        } else {
          $searchResultWrap.closest('div').hide();
        }
      }, 500));

      $menuSearchValue.on('keydown', function (e) {
        var $li;
        var $liOn;
        if (e.keyCode === 13 || e.keyCode === 38 || e.keyCode === 40) {
          e.preventDefault();
          $li = $searchResultWrap.find('li[data-menu-id]');
          $liOn = $searchResultWrap.find('li.on[data-menu-id]');
        }

        // 엔터
        if (e.keyCode === 13) {
          if ($liOn.length > 0) {
            openView($liOn.data('menu-id'));
          } else {
            $('#jsMdiMenuSearchButton').click();
          }
        }

        // ESC
        if (e.keyCode === 27) {
          $searchResultWrap.closest('div').hide();
        }

        // 방향키 위
        if (e.keyCode === 38) {
          if ($liOn.length > 0) {
            if ($liOn.eq(0).prev().length) {
              $liOn.eq(0).removeClass('on');
              $liOn.eq(0).prev().addClass('on');
              $liOn.eq(0).prev()[0].scrollIntoView(false);
            }
          }
        }

        // 방향키 아래
        if (e.keyCode === 40) {
          if ($li.length > 0) {
            if ($liOn.length > 0) {
              if ($liOn.eq(0).next().length > 0) {
                $liOn.eq(0).removeClass('on');
                $liOn.eq(0).next().addClass('on');
                $liOn.eq(0).next()[0].scrollIntoView(false);
              }
            } else {
              $li.eq(0).addClass('on');
            }
          }
        }
      });

      $(document).on('click', function (e) {
        var $target = $(e.target);
        if ($target.closest('.lnb_search').length === 0 && $target.closest('.lnb_searched').length === 0) {
          $searchResultWrap.closest('div').hide();
        }
      });

      $('#jsMdiMenuSearchButton').on('click', function () {
        var value = $menuSearchValue.val().trim();
        if (!value) {
          alert(mdc.lang.getMessage('MG026')); //검색어를 입력하세요.
          return;
        }

        value = getMenuIdByValue(value);
        if (!value) {
          alert(mdc.lang.getMessage('MO045')); //일치하는 메뉴가 없습니다.
          return;
        }

        openView(value);
      });

      $searchResultWrap.on('click', 'li[data-menu-id]', function () {
        openView($(this).data('menu-id'));
      });

      // 전체 탭 닫기 이벤트
      $('#jsCloseAllViewsButton').on('click', function () {
        self.mdi.closeAllViews();
        /*
        if ($('#jsViewSizeButton').hasClass('size_max')) {
          $('#jsViewSizeButton').click();
        }
        */
      });

      // MDI 확대/축소 이벤트
      $('#jsViewSizeButton').on('click', function () {
        if ($('#jsViewSizeButton').hasClass('size_max')) {
          $('.btn_content_size_btn').removeClass('size_max');
          $('.btn_lnb').removeClass('size_max');
          $('.container').removeClass('size_max');
          if($('#jsMdiMenuButton').hasClass('hide')){
            $('.content').css('width', 'calc(100% - 40px)');
          }else{
            $('.content').css('width', 'calc(100% - 240px)');
          }
          if (ci.agent.isIe === true) {
            $('.bottomround').css('width', '200px');
          }
          $('.header').show();
          self.mdi.contractView();
        } else {
          $('.btn_content_size_btn').addClass('size_max');
          $('.btn_lnb').addClass('size_max');
          $('.container').addClass('size_max');
          if ($('#jsMdiMenuButton').hasClass('hide')) {
            $('.content').css('width', 'calc(100% - 40px)');
          } else {
            $('.content').css('width', 'calc(100% - 240px)');
          }
          if (ci.agent.isIe === true) {
            $('.bottomround').css('width', '200px');
          }
          $('.header').hide();
          self.mdi.expandView();
        }
      });

      $('#jsMdiTabListButton').on('click', function () {
        var $tabList = $('.CI-MDI-TAB-LIST');
        if (!$tabList.hasClass('active')) {
          $tabList.find('ul').empty();
          var views = self.mdi.getViews();
          views.forEach(function (view) {
            self.mdi.appendTabList(view);
          });
        }
        $tabList.toggleClass('active');
      });

      $('.CI-MDI-TAB-LIST').on('click', 'a', function () {
        var menuId = $(this).closest('li').attr('data-menu-id');
        self.mdi.openView(menuId);
      });

      $('.CI-MDI-TAB-LIST').on('click', 'button', function () {
        var menuId = $(this).closest('li').attr('data-menu-id');
        self.mdi.closeView(menuId);
      });

      // 메뉴 열기/닫기 이벤트
      $('#jsMdiMenuButton').on('click', function () {
        var containerWidth = $('.container').width();
        if ($('#jsMdiMenuButton').hasClass('hide')) {
          $('.btn_lnb').removeClass('hide');
          $('.content').removeClass('size_max');
          $('.lnb > .lnb_search, .lnb > .lnb_tree').animate({left:0}, 500);
          $('.btn_lnb').animate({left:200}, 500);
          $('.lnb').animate({width:200}, 500);
          $('.bottomround').show();
          $('.content').animate({width: containerWidth - 240}, 500, function () {
            $(this).css('width', 'calc(100% - 240px)');
            self.mdi.showMenu();
          });
        } else {
          $('.btn_lnb').addClass('hide');
          $('.content').addClass('size_max');
          $('.lnb > .lnb_search, .lnb > .lnb_tree').animate({left:-200}, 500);
          $('.btn_lnb').animate({left:0}, 500);
          $('.lnb').animate({width:0}, 500);
          setTimeout(function () {
            $('.bottomround').hide();
          }, 500);
          $('.content').animate({width: containerWidth - 40}, 500, function () {
            $(this).css('width', 'calc(100% - 40px)');
            self.mdi.hideMenu();
          });
        }
      });

      // 검색조건 및 footer 열기 / 닫기
      $('#jsMdiContent').on('click', '.CI-MDI-COMPONENT-BUTTON', function () {
        var $this = $(this);
        var $div = $this.siblings('div');
        if ($div.is(':visible')) {
          $div.hide();
          if ($div.data('component') === 'search') {
            $this.addClass('on2');
            $this.text('Open');
          } else {
            $this.closest('.CI-MDI-COMPONENT-FOOTER').addClass('on2');
            $this.text('Open');
          }
        } else {
          $div.show();
          if ($div.data('component') === 'search') {
            $this.removeClass('on2');
            $this.text('Close');
          } else {
            $this.closest('.CI-MDI-COMPONENT-FOOTER').removeClass('on2');
            $this.text('Close');
          }
        }

        if ($div.data('component') === 'search') {
          self.mdi.triggerModuleEvent();
        }
      });

      // 브라우저 리사이징 이벤트
      api.util.addEvent(window, 'resize', _.debounce(function () {
        self.mdi.triggerModuleEvent();
      }, 500));

    }
  });
</script>
<!--b:e-->
        </section>
        <!-- //CONTENT -->
      </section>
			
    
    <!-- //CONTAINER -->
